1. Simple syntax

xyplot(mpg ~ wt | as.factor(cyl), data = mtcars)

vs.

par(mfrow = c(1,3))
plot(mtcars$wt[mtcars$cyl == 4], mtcars$mpg[mtcars$cyl == 4])
plot(mtcars$wt[mtcars$cyl == 6], mtcars$mpg[mtcars$cyl == 6])
plot(mtcars$wt[mtcars$cyl == 8], mtcars$mpg[mtcars$cyl == 8])
